    # game/traveling.rpy:843
    old "You’re squeezed between the hills and the forests. The only larger beast you spot is a single saurian basking on a boulder, lazily observing you from a safe distance. Your ears catch the howls coming from the north, long and loud, and as you keep an eye on the rock ledges, you almost miss the drastic shift in the landscape. The forest turns into a lake, and the few plants growing next to the road mostly bear fruit. The road is not as reliable here as it was in the hills. Parts of it are a bit muddy, and the puddles disturb your ride. "
    new ""

    # game/traveling.rpy:843
    old "Maybe the locals will maintain it before it gets swallowed by the lake."
    new ""

    # game/traveling.rpy:853
    old "You’re squeezed between the hills and the forests. The only larger beast you spot is a single saurian basking on a boulder, lazily observing you from a safe distance. Your ears catch the howls coming from the north, long and loud, while you look at the lake, hoping there’s no threat hiding below the water surface. The few plants growing next to the road mostly bear fruit. \n\nThe road is not as reliable here as it was at the eastern bank. Parts of it are a bit muddy, and the puddles disturb your ride. "
